                <head>544. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>According to telegram 18, July 14, Ambassador <persName corresp="#p_MID1"
                        >McIntosh</persName> extended to President <persName corresp="#p_BBL1"
                        >Batlle</persName> an invitation from President <persName corresp="#p_EDD1"
                        >Eisenhower</persName> to visit the United States. (Department of State,
                    Central Files, 733.11/7–1455) <persName corresp="#p_BBL1">Batlle</persName>
                    visited the United States December 5–17. See <ref target="#d548">Documents
                        548</ref>, <ref target="#d549">549</ref>, and <ref target="#d550"
                    >550</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
